l Hasan of the Institute for Development Economics and Finance said the government should change its state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  assumptions soon, instead of waiting until July.   \par \par \uc2 Under current regulations, the government reviews its state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  assumptions at the end of the first semester, considering factors such as \b \highlight22\uc2 expenditure\b0 \highlight\uc2  and revenue, the \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2 , global oil prices, the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 's interest rate, inflation rate and the rupiah exchange rate.   \par \par \uc2 The review is to ensure that the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is on track.   \par \par \uc2 If deemed necessary, \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  revisions will be made, with the approval of the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 Economist M. Ikhsan Modjo said the government should revise the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  by cutting the fuel \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and allocating the money to ensure the supply of staple foodstuffs, which have experienced price rices in recent weeks.   \par \par \uc2 Responding to the suggestions, Sri Mulyani said the government would continue to maintain the targets set out under the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 "This does not mean that the government responds slowly, it is just that we need to study every \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , especially those relating to costs," she said.   \par \par \uc2 "What is important is that we have to make sure that the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  is below the line."   \par \par \uc2 The government has projected a \b \highlight22\uc2 budget deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  at 1.7 percent of gross domestic product, or Rp 74 trillion. (adt)   